beer.beer_description:
No better way to celebrate the Holiday season, then with a big sweet Imperial Pastry Stout brimming with notes of chocolate, vanilla, cinnamon, milk sugar and cake batter.

A pure expression of dessert, not just for consuming out of a can or glass. Feel free to pour over ice cream and if adding to homemade desserts, remember to add to batter slowly.

That's 405 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 82! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

items.badge_description: Porters and Stouts are rich with both history and flavor. Roasty, dark, and delicious, these two styles helped start it all. That’s 105 different beers with the style of Porter or Stout. Try 5 more for Level 22!

When a single isn’t enough, make it a double. Doubling the hops and malts in a recipe results in a higher ABV and can pack quite a boozey punch. That's 145 different beers with the style that contains Imperial / Double in its style name. Try 5 more for Level 30!

items.badge_name: Beyond a Shadow of a Stout (Level 17)
items.badge_description: We all love Stouts, and now we have a dedicated badge to celebrate your dedication to these dark, top-fermented beer in multiple variations, like Oatmeal, Milk and more! Which one will you start with? That's 85 different beers with the style of Stout. Try 5 more for Level 18!
